007package violajones_utils;
008
009import ij.IJ;
010import ij.plugin.PlugIn;
011import imagingbook.core.plugin.JavaDocHelp;
012import imagingbook.violajones.data.HaarTrainingSet;
013
014/**
015 * ImageJ plugin. 
016 * @author WB
017 *
018 */
019public class List_Haar_Cascade_Files implements PlugIn, JavaDocHelp {
020
021        public void run(String arg0) {
022                for (HaarTrainingSet s : HaarTrainingSet.values()) {
023                        IJ.log("Haar set type (enum) = " + s.toString());
024                        IJ.log("   full path   = " + s.getURL());
025                        IJ.log("");
026                }
027        }
028
029}
